Reactions trailed as Nigerian Politician and Ovation Publisher, Dele Momodu took to his Instagram page to share few minutes video of National Leader of All Progressive Congress (APC) and Presidential Aspirant, Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu with Nuhu Ribadu and others in Mecca, Saudi Arabia. They were seen together in the video gisting and laughing.
Bola Ahmed Tinubu is a Popular Nigerian politician, father, Accountant, former Governor of Lagos State, and social media personality who used to post lovely pictures and messages on Instagram. He is one of the most versatile and popular politicians in Nigeria.
He has made his intention known to contest for the President of the Federal Republic of Nigeria in the coming Presidential elections, year 2023. He holds chieftaincies titles as Asiwaju of Lagos State and Jagaban of the Borgu Kingdom. He is well known for his roles in Nigerian politics and his political party. He is married to his beautiful wife, Remi Tinubu who is currently a Senator in the National Assembly. Their union is blessed with lovely children.
